something_else_ep = EntryPoint('something_else', 'mlblocks.__version__')
primitives_ep = EntryPoint('primitives', 'tests.test_discovery', attrs=[
    'FAKE_PRIMITIVES_PATH'], dist=Distribution())
another_primitives_ep = EntryPoint('primitives', 'tests.test_discovery',
    attrs=['FAKE_PRIMITIVES_PATHS'], dist=Distribution())
iep_mock.return_value = [something_else_ep, primitives_ep,
    another_primitives_ep]
paths = discovery._load_entry_points('primitives')
expected = ['this/is/a/fake', 'this/is/another/fake',
    'this/is/yet/another/fake']
assert paths == expected
expected_calls = [call('mlblocks')]
assert iep_mock.call_args_list == expected_calls
patch('mlblocks.discovery.pkg_resources.iter_entry_points')
